metadata.name: Elegance
metadata.description: Graceful and mysterious, loyal and reliable, smart and kind. And if man is the crown of nature, then the horse is certainly its masterpiece. They radiate warmth, energy, have a whole range of feelings: joy, fear, curiosity. And, as a person, they have their own personality. Indeed, since ancient times, the horse has been a faithful and indispensable companion of man.
